n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">810058448255</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KID’S KARAOKE FUN - Kidplokio Rockin’ Star karaoke machine comes with everything a kid needs to put on their very own musical performance; a real working microphone with a mic stand that has realistic sound effects</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">MP3 CONNECTION -  Connect your MP3 player to the sing along karaoke machine so your child can play their favorite songs and practice their rock star skills; encourages creativity and imagination</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SHUTDOWN MODE - Karaoke machine automatically shuts down after 5 minutes with no use (except for MP3 mode) to conserve energy; Requires (3) AA batteries, not included</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE AND KID-SAFE - Made of high-quality, durable plastic that can be wiped clean and dried as needed; Safe for children ages 3 and up with parental supervision</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - Colors: blue, white, yellow; Sound effect buttons: yes; Material: plastic: Batteries required: (3) AA, not included; Shutdown mode: yes; Recommended age: 3 years and up</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Kidplokio Musical Microphone Pretend Play Karaoke Machine Kids MP3 Player</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">49.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Is your child a budding rock star? The Kidplokio Rockin’ Star karaoke machine is a great gift idea for your little one! It comes with everything a kid needs to put on their own musical performance - a real working karaoke microphone with a mic stand and realistic sound effect buttons. \n\nIn addition to the above features, this fantastic karaoke machine comes with an MP3 connection so you can plug your MP3 in and play your child’s favorite songs so they can sing along! Singing and dancing is also a great way for children to practice their creativity, and imagination and get some fun indoor exercise.\n\nOur unique pretend play musical toy comes with an automatic shutdown mode - the karaoke machine will turn off by itself after 5 minutes of no use to conserve energy. The machine requires (3) AA batteries (not included).\n\nMade of high-quality, durable plastic, this machine can easily be wiped down and dried off as needed to keep it clean in between uses. It comes with a cardboard box so you can pack it up to store for later use. These machines are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision, so grab one of these for your little one and watch them star in their own shows!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>